"A.D.2028/3/30/13:00": "This... is more than I was expecting. We had not yet considered this far into this case."
"If they're wise, they won't approach. My job is nothing to do with them, it is simply to collect that child."
"In just one strike... My army's gone!?"
"Mother, this isn't what we discussed. I might be good at handling irregularities, but I still have my limits."
"Additional charges won't make up for this... I wouldn't even settle for an offer of new technology!"
"...I'll fight too. No, let me fight with you."
